title: You wont want to miss this! Res Lease in Round Rock. 2 Beds, 2 Baths
posting_body: You can't miss this fantastic opportunity!
The superb 2-bedroom, 2-bathroom condominium in Round Rock, TX, is just waiting for you!
Minutes from I35 shopping and access to major retail, dining, and entertainment outlets.
You'll enjoy everything this lovely home offers, from its spacious rooms and big windows that allow in tons of sunlight to the beautiful living room with refined wooden flooring and gas fireplace.
Master bedroom has vaulted ceilings and exposed beams with stacked washer and dryer close by.
Brand new flooring throughout.

This condo has an elegant kitchen with white cabinetry, where you'll find plenty of counter and storage space, a pantry, and stainless steel appliances, waiting for the home chef to create some beautiful memories.
Lovely afternoons will be enjoyed in your private backyard with deck and outdoor lighting; perfect for exercising, having some friends over, or just relaxing after a long day at work!
